  "description": "Open DAMOS for Bosch EDC17_C50 (TriCore, little-endian). Generated from the manufacturer DAMOS (ASAP2 A2L, project X_7HH21) + matching ROM via scripts/damos_a2l_to_opendamos.py. STD_AXIS maps carry an inline (nx,ny) header (NO_AXIS_PTS) so fingerprint relocation works across firmware variants. 12 tuning maps (driver's wish, injection timing, rail pressure, smoke limiter, air, injector trim).",
